System Modules

The system is divided into the following modules. Each module serves a specific purpose.

| Module | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| User and Role Management | Creating accounts, assigning roles, login and logout. |
| Internship Placement | Recording where each student is placed, with which supervisor and for what period. |
| Weekly Logbook | Students write their weekly activity logs here. The log goes through a review process. |
| Supervisor Review Workflow | Workplace supervisors review submitted logs and approve or return them. |
| Academic Evaluation | Academic supervisors score students at the end of the internship. |
| Score Computation | The system automatically calculates the final score from the criteria scores. |
| Dashboards and Reports | Each role sees a summary of their tasks. Admin can generate full reports. |



